Class Packman

  • java.lang.Object
    • game_elements.Packman

  • public class Packman
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a packman. Including the gps point, speed radius and orientation (right or left) of the packman.
    Author:
    Eitan Lichtman, Netanel Indik
